    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example benefits from a comprehensive VANOS service and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the primary structural concerns of the chassis. The six-speed manual gearbox shifts with precision, and the factory variable M differential lock provides predictable traction under load. Suspension has been updated with Bilstein B6 dampers to maintain the original handling geometry while improving damping frequency. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use, the drivetrain and cooling system are in robust health, making this a mechanically sound example of BMW's analog performance peak.",
